article_title: Pyotr Mamonov, Russian rock musician and actor, dies at 70
meta_description: MOSCOW (AP) — Pyotr Mamonov, a rock musician, poet and actor who was a prominent figure in Russia's cultural scene for decades, has died. He was 70.
